      <body>
        <div xml:id="song23">
          <head rend="italic"><hi rend="roman">Cælia</hi> singing.</head>
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
          <div type="underlay">
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l>Till I beheld fair <hi rend="italic">Calia's</hi> face,</l>
            <l rend="indent1">where perfect Beauty keeps her Court,</l>
            <l>a Lovers passion found no place</l>
            <l rend="indent1">in me, who counted Love a sport:</l>
            <l>I thought the whole world could not move,</l>
            <l>a well resolved heart to love.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l>Wounded by her I now adore</l>
            <l rend="indent1">Those pow'rs of Love I have defi'd,</l>
            <l>I court the flames I scorn'd before</l>
            <l rend="indent1">And am repayd with Scorn and Pride:</l>
            <l>I such unpitty'd Flames to dwell,</l>
            <l>Is not a Martrydome, but Hell.</l>
          </lg>
            <lg type="stanza">
              <l><hi rend="italic">Cupid</hi> can't help me, nor wound her,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">He'l rather prove my Rivall hence,</l>
              <l>Though blind he'l turn Idolater,</l>
              <l rend="indent1">For she hath Charms for ev'ry sence;</l>
              <l>Shoud he her voyce's musick heare,</l>
              <l>Soft Love would enter Love's own Eare.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
        </div>
      </body>
